# bonsAI — bootstrap only

- Configure MCP server `bonsai` (see [docs/mcp-setup.md](docs/mcp-setup.md)).
- At session start or before non-trivial work: call **`bonsai.session.bootstrap`**.
- For Deck UI/RPC edits: call **`bonsai.workflow.get`** with `id=deck-dev-loop`; use **decky-plugin-studio** for deploy/preview.
- Specialist reviews: MCP prompt **`bonsai/persona/{name}`** (`security-auditor`, `master-debugger`, `red-team`, `blue-team`, `foss-advocate`, `refactor-specialist`).
- Full policies, workflows, and personas live in **`packages/bonsai-mcp/knowledge/`** — do not duplicate here.
